  section#privacy-policy.privacy-policy
  .container
    h2.text-center Privacy Policy
    p This privacy policy applies to artiosdev.com
    .row
      .lead.col-lg-10
        h4 What information do we collect?
        p
          |ArtiosDev collects non-personally identifying information such as browser type, operating system, referring site, and the date and time of each site 
          |visit. We may also collect personal information that you volunteer when you respond to a survey, or fill out a form.
        h3 How do we use your information?
        p
          | ArtiosDev’s primary purpose in collecting non-personally identifying information is to better understand how visitors use our web site. Information we 
          |collect may be used:
        ul
          li To personalise your experience
          li To improve our web site
          li To write and publish reports or blog posts that include aggregate data.

        p
          |If you choose to provide your email address, we may use it to send you information and respond to inquiries.

        h4 Do we use cookies?
        p
          |Yes. A cookie is a string of information that a web site stores on a visitor’s computer and that the visitor’s browser provides to the web site each 
          |time the visitor returns. ArtiosDev uses cookies to identify visitors and to track their usage of our web site. Visitors who do not wish to have cookies
          | placed on their computer should disable cookies within their browser before using our web site.

        h4 Do we disclose any personal information to outside parties?
        p 
          |We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personally identifying information to outside parties.
        p 
          |We do reserve the right to access and/or disclose personally identifying information and non-personal information as required by courts or administrative agencies.
        h4 Online Privacy Policy Only
        p 
          |This online privacy policy applies only to information collected through our web site and not to information collected offline.
        h4 Your Consent
        p 
          |By using our site, you consent to our online privacy policy.
